# ⚡ Blink Insurance – AI-Powered Parametric Income Protection

> **Hackathon MVP · Phase 1 · Frontend Prototype**

A visually impressive React Native + Expo mobile app that demonstrates AI-powered parametric insurance for gig workers (delivery partners like Swiggy/Zomato).

---

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
npm install --legacy-peer-deps

# Start Expo development server
npx expo start

# Run on Android
npx expo start --android

# Run on iOS
npx expo start --ios
```

---

## 📁 Project Structure

```
GUIDEWIRE_BLINK/
├── App.js                    ← Root entry point
├── app.json                  ← Expo configuration
├── babel.config.js           ← Babel + NativeWind setup
├── tailwind.config.js        ← Tailwind CSS config
│
├── navigation/
│   ├── AppNavigator.jsx      ← Root Stack navigator (Splash → Onboarding → Main)
│   └── TabNavigator.jsx      ← Bottom tab bar (Home, Risk, Alerts, Claims, Profile)
│
├── screens/
│   ├── SplashScreen.jsx      ← Animated logo + gradient bg (auto-navigates)
│   ├── WelcomeScreen.jsx     ← Hero landing with feature cards
│   ├── OnboardingScreen.jsx  ← 4-step worker profile form
│   ├── HomeScreen.jsx        ← Main dashboard
│   ├── RiskAnalysisScreen.jsx← AI risk score breakdown + charts
│   ├── DisruptionAlertsScreen.jsx ← Live disruption alerts with filters
│   ├── ClaimsScreen.jsx      ← Claims history + simulation
│   ├── InsurancePlanScreen.jsx ← Pricing cards for 3 plans
│   └── ProfileScreen.jsx     ← Worker profile + settings
│
├── components/
│   ├── GradientHeader.jsx       ← Reusable gradient header bar
│   ├── AnimatedProgressRing.jsx ← SVG circular progress with animation
│   ├── RiskScoreCard.jsx        ← AI risk score display card
│   ├── InsurancePlanCard.jsx    ← Pricing card for insurance plans
│   ├── AlertCard.jsx            ← Disruption alert card with pulse
│   ├── ClaimCard.jsx            ← Auto-claim payout card
│   ├── StatsCard.jsx            ← Compact metric tile
│   └── WorkerProfileCard.jsx    ← Worker details card
│
├── constants/
│   ├── colors.js   ← Full color palette, typography, spacing constants
│   └── theme.js    ← Risk levels, severity configs, utility functions
│
├── data/
│   └── mockData.js ← All simulated data (worker, risk, alerts, claims, plans)
│
├── hooks/
│   └── useAnimations.js ← Reanimated hooks (card, pulse, slide, countUp)
│
├── services/
│   └── riskCalculator.js ← AI risk score simulator + payout calculator
│
└── assets/          ← App icons and splash images
```

