## 📱 Screens Overview

### 1. Splash Screen
- Animated logo reveal with spring physics
- Floating purple particles
- Pulsing ring animation
- Auto-navigates to Welcome after 2.8s

### 2. Welcome Screen
- Hero headline with purple gradient text
- 4 feature cards (2×2 grid)
- Social proof stats (50K+ Workers, <2min payout)
- CTA button → Onboarding

### 3. Onboarding (4 Steps)
- Step 1: Name input
- Step 2: Platform (Swiggy/Zomato/etc) + Vehicle type chip selection
- Step 3: City picker
- Step 4: Working hours selection
- Animated progress bar + step indicators

### 4. Home Dashboard
- Worker greeting + active policy banner
- AI Risk Score card (animated progress ring)
- 2×2 stats grid (protected income, payouts, claims, alerts)
- Weekly earnings bar chart (color-coded days)
- Active disruption alerts preview
- Quick action tiles (View Plans, File Claim)

### 5. Risk Analysis
- Large animated ring (170px) with overall score
- 5 risk factors with progress bars (Weather, Pollution, Disruption, Traffic, Demand)
- 7-day dual bar chart (risk vs earnings)
- AI recommendation insight card

### 6. Disruption Alerts
- Summary banner (active count, max payout, total this week)
- Filter chips (All, Active, Weather, Pollution, Disruption)
- Alert cards with severity badges, pulse dots, payout estimates
- "How Auto-Claims Work" explainer box

### 7. Claims & Payouts
- Total received / total claims / avg settlement summary
- **Claim Simulation** – tap to run animated 4-step auto-claim
- Claims history with timeline view
- ROI net benefit card

### 8. Insurance Plans
- 3 pricing cards (Basic ₹39, Pro ₹79, Elite ₹129)
- Gradient cards with feature lists
- "Pro Guard" highlighted as Most Popular
- Plan summary + Activate CTA

### 9. Profile
- Worker card with initials avatar, platform badge, rating
- Stats row (days protected, net benefit, total premium)
- Menu sections: Insurance, Earnings, Preferences, Support
- Toggle switches for notifications and dark mode

---

## 🎭 Animations

| Animation | Where Used | Library |
|---|---|---|
| Animated progress ring | Risk score cards | Reanimated + SVG |
| Spring card entrance | All cards | Reanimated withSpring |
| Pulse dot | Active alerts | Reanimated withRepeat |
| Slide-in entrance | Alert cards | Reanimated translateX |
| Step-by-step simulation | Claims screen | setTimeout + Animated |
| Hero text entrance | Welcome screen | Animated API |
| Logo reveal | Splash screen | Animated API |
| Floating particles | Splash screen | Animated loop |

