## 🛠 Tech Stack

| Technology | Version | Usage |
|---|---|---|
| React Native | 0.74 | Core framework |
| Expo | ~51 | Build toolchain |
| React Navigation | v6 | Stack + Bottom tabs |
| Expo Linear Gradient | ~13 | All gradient UI |
| React Native Reanimated | ~3.10 | Smooth animations |
| React Native SVG | 15.2 | Progress rings |
| Lucide React Native | ^0.395 | Icon system |
| NativeWind | ^2.0 | Tailwind styling |
| React Native Chart Kit | ^6.12 | Charts |

